# 🔍 Roland Discord Bot — Full Audit Report

> Scope: Consistency, Security, User Experience, Admin Experience, Architecture
> Date: 2026-04-09 | Repository: `roland-discord-bot`

---

## Executive Summary

The codebase is a **mature, feature-rich Discord bot** with a multi-tenant SaaS architecture ("Guild Pilot"), a comprehensive admin dashboard, and deep Solana blockchain integration. It has strong foundational patterns (centralized logger, module gating, tenant isolation, API response envelopes) but suffers from **branding fragmentation**, **inconsistent API response patterns**, a **monolithic server.js file (5,000 lines)**, and several unresolved findings from the March 2026 security audit. The project is usable but needs a focused cleanup sprint before scaling.

---

## 1. 🔐 Security

### 1.1 Unresolved Findings from Previous Audit (2026-03-28)

A [previous security audit](file:///c:/Users/Roland/OneDrive%20-%20Kleermaker/Cartoon%20Maffia%20DAO/roland-discord-bot/SECURITY_AUDIT_2026-03-28.md) identified 20 findings. Based on the current codebase review, several **remain unresolved**:

| # | Finding | Status | Priority |
|---|---------|--------|----------|
| 1 | DOM XSS via unescaped `innerHTML` in portal.js | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🔴 Critical |
| 3 | CDN script loaded without SRI hash (`@solana/web3.js@latest`) | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🔴 High |
| 5 | Battle lobby race condition (check-then-act) | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🟡 Medium |
| 6 | `MOCK_MODE=true` in prod auto-verifies users | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🟡 Medium-High |
| 8 | `governance.js` imports settings.json statically | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🟡 Medium |
| 11 | No CSRF protection on admin API routes | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🟡 Medium |
| 13 | Logger has no level gating | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🟢 Low |
| 15 | Dead `ogConfig.js` command still registered | ⚠️ **Still present** | 🟢 Low |

### 1.2 New Security Observations

| Issue | Location | Severity |
|-------|----------|----------|
| **Hardcoded default session secret** — `'solpranos-secret-key-change-this-in-production'` used as fallback | [server.js:291](file:///c:/Users/Roland/OneDrive%20-%20Kleermaker/Cartoon%20Maffia%20DAO/roland-discord-bot/web/server.js#L291), [index.js:39](file:///c:/Users/Roland/OneDrive%20-%20Kleermaker/Cartoon%20Maffia%20DAO/roland-discord-bot/index.js#L39) | 🔴 Critical |
| **`SOLPRANOS` in wallet verification message** — Hardcoded project name in a multi-tenant signature message | [server.js:3957](file:///c:/Users/Roland/OneDrive%20-%20Kleermaker/Cartoon%20Maffia%20DAO/roland-discord-bot/web/server.js#L3957) | 🟡 Medium |
| **Error messages leak internals to Discord** — `error.message` sent directly in command catch blocks | Multiple command files | 🟡 Medium |
| **`.gitignore` is too minimal** — Missing entries for `logs/`, `*.log`, `.env.*`, `config/settings.json`, `config/module-toggles.json`, OS files (`.DS_Store`, `Thumbs.db`) | [.gitignore](file:///c:/Users/Roland/OneDrive%20-%20Kleermaker/Cartoon%20Maffia%20DAO/roland-discord-bot/.gitignore) | 🟡 Medium |
| **Raw `console.error` in service code** — Bypasses logger in `gameNightService.js:184` | [gameNightService.js:184](file:///c:/Users/Roland/OneDrive%20-%20Kleermaker/Cartoon%20Maffia%20DAO/roland-discord-bot/services/gameNightService.js#L184) | 🟢 Low |

### 1.3 What's Working Well ✅
- `moduleGate` enforces permission checks before every command and API route
- `superadminGuard` isolates sensitive admin endpoints
- Wallet linking uses SQLite transactions to prevent race conditions
- Helius API has rate-limiting built into the NFT service
- `apiResponse.sanitize()` strips sensitive fields from API responses
- Session store is persistent (better-sqlite3) — not in-memory
- ESLint config includes `eslint-plugin-security` rules

